0.1.name: wordpress/wp-worker-catalog
0.1.description:
This plugin is created for manpower placement agencies to have an online catalog of their people, so that employers can browse and see if their skill sets fit their needs.

Visit http://www.ardeearam.com/wp-worker-catalog/ for more information.

Visit http://manpower.ardeearam.com/ for demo.

Explore the administration panel at http://manpower.ardeearam.com/wp-admin/
